			voluptatum!.</p>

		</div>

		<div class=" col-12 col-md-4 p-2 "><img class="img-fluid m-2" src="{{ asset('/assets/img/room-key-svgrepo-com.svg')}}" style='width: 10rem' >
		<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Aliquid doloremque ducimus eaque earum error eum inventore magnam,
			maiores porro repellendus repudiandae tenetur ullam voluptates! Consequuntur cumque debitis iusto, modi nostrum odio porro
			reprehenderit tempore voluptatem.</p>

		</div>
		<div class="col-12 col-md-4 p-2 "><img class="img-fluid m-2" src="{{ asset('/assets/img/spa-svgrepo-com.svg')}}" style='width: 10rem' >
